com.ibm.wala.dataflow.IFDS

Class BackwardsSupergraph<T,P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.wala.dataflow.IFDS.BackwardsSupergraph<T,P>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ISupergraph<T,P>, EdgeManager<T>, Graph<T>, NodeManager<T>, NumberedEdgeManager<T>, NumberedGraph<T>, NumberedNodeManager<T>, java.lang.Iterable<T>

    public class BackwardsSupergraph<T,P>
extends java.lang.Object
implements ISupergraph<T,P>
    A "reversed" supergraph for backwards analysis.

    In this view, a return is treated like a call, and vice-versa. All normal edges are reversed.
